X11-FullScreen version 0.01
===========================

Provides a very simple Xlib interface capable of creating borderless
windows taking up an entire screen of an X windows display.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  X11

